2 hal hen, ya to SSH key k zarye (jo k isi repo ki file <github initial setup> me h.
or dusra tareeqa:
open .git/config
add these line to the end for the repo(my_repo):
[remote "origin"]
	url = https://amirsaleem1990:my_password@github.com/amirsaleem1990/my_repo.git
[credential]
	helper = store
  
  
  
git config credential.helper store
git pull # this will pull the repo, and for furter push for this repo git no require password
